ck, California|Turlock]] || [[California]] || [[California Collegiate Athletic Association]]\n|-bgcolor=#ffa0a0\n| scope=row| {{sort|California, San Diego|[[University of California, San Diego]]}}\n| [[UC San Diego Tritons|Tritons]] || [[La Jolla]] || [[California]] || [[California Collegiate Athletic Association]]{{efn|group=Full|UC San Diego will begin a transition to [[NCAA Division I]] in 2020, joining the [[Big West Conference]].}}\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Cameron University]]\n| [[Cameron Aggies|Aggies]] || [[Lawton, Oklahoma|Lawton]] || [[Oklahoma]] || [[Lone Star Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Carson\u2013Newman University]]\n| [[Carson\u2013Newman Eagles|Eagles]] || [[Jefferson City, Tennessee|Jefferson City]] || [[Tennessee]] || [[South Atlantic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Catawba College]]\n| Indians || [[Salisbury, North Carolina|Salisbury]] || [[North Carolina]] || [[South Atlantic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Cedarville University]]\n| [[Cedarville University Yellow Jackets|Yellow Jackets]] || [[Cedarville, Ohio|Cedarville]] || [[Ohio]] || [[Great Midwest Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Central Missouri|[[University of Central Missouri]]}}\n| [[Central Missouri Mules and Jennies|Mules & Jennies]] || [[Warrensburg, Missouri|Warrensburg]] || [[Missouri]] || [[Mid-America Intercollegiate Athletics Association]]\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Central Oklahoma|[[University of Central Oklahoma]]}}\n| [[Central Oklahoma Bronchos|Bronchos]] || [[Edmond, Oklahoma|Edmond]] || [[Oklahoma]] || [[Mid-America Intercollegiate Athletics Association]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Central State University]]\n| Marauders & Lady Marauders || [[Wilberforce, Ohio|Wilberforce]] || [[Ohio]] || [[Southern Intercollegiate Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Central Washington University]]\n| [[Central Washington Wildcats|Wildcats]] || [[Ellensburg, Washington|Ellensburg]] || [[Washington (state)|Washington]] || [[Great Northwest Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Chadron State College]]\n| [[Chadron State Eagles|Eagles]] || [[Chadron, Nebraska|Chadron]] || [[Nebraska]] || [[Rocky Mountain Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Chaminade University of Honolulu]]\n| [[Chaminade Silverswords|Silverswords]] || [[Honolulu]] || [[Hawaii|Hawai'i]] || [[Pacific West Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Charleston|[[University of Charleston]]}}\n| [[Charleston Golden Eagles|Golden Eagles]] || [[Charleston, West Virginia|Charleston]] || [[West Virginia]] || [[Mountain East Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Chestnut Hill College]]\n| Griffins || [[Philadelphia]] || [[Pennsylvania]] || [[Central Atlantic Collegiate Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Chowan University]]\n| [[Chowan Hawks|Hawks]] || [[Murfreesboro, North Carolina|Murfreesboro]] || [[North Carolina]] || [[Conference Carolinas]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Christian Brothers University]]\n| [[Christian Brothers Buccaneers|Buccaneers]] || [[Memphis, Tennessee|Memphis]] || [[Tennessee]] || [[Gulf South Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Claflin University]]\n| Panthers || [[Orangeburg, South Carolina|Orangeburg]] || [[South Carolina]] || [[Central Intercollegiate Athletic Association]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Clarion University of Pennsylvania]]\n| [[Clarion Golden Eagles|Golden Eagles]] || [[Clarion, Pennsylvania|Clarion]] || [[Pennsylvania]] || [[Pennsylvania State Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Clark Atlanta University]]\n| [[Clark Atlanta Panthers|Panthers]] || [[Atlanta]] || [[Georgia (U.S. state)|Georgia]] || [[Southern Intercollegiate Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Clayton State University]]\n| [[Clayton State Lakers|Lakers]] || [[Morrow, Georgia|Morrow]] || [[Georgia (U.S. state)|Georgia]] || [[Peach Belt Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Coker College]]\n| Cobras || [[Hartsville, South Carolina|Hartsville]] || [[South Carolina]] || [[South Atlantic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Colorado Christian University]]\n| [[Colorado Christian Cougars|Cougars]] || [[Lakewood, Color