ida]] || [[Sunshine State Conference]]\n|-bgcolor=#ffa0a0\n|scope=row| [[Tarleton State University]]\n| [[Tarleton State Texans|Texans]] || [[Stephenville, Texas|Stephenville]] || [[Texas]] || [[Lone Star Conference]]{{efn|group=Full|name=\"WAC 2020\"}}\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Texas A&M Commerce|[[Texas A&M University\u2013Commerce]]}}\n| [[Texas A&M\u2013Commerce Lions|Lions]] || [[Commerce, Texas|Commerce]] || [[Texas]] || [[Lone Star Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Texas A&M Kingsville|[[Texas A&M University\u2013Kingsville]]}}\n| [[Texas A&M\u2013Kingsville Javelinas|Javelinas]] || [[Kingsville, Texas|Kingsville]] || [[Texas]] || [[Lone Star Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Texas A&M International University]]\n| [[Texas A&M International Dustdevils|Dustdevils]] || [[Laredo, Texas|Laredo]] || [[Texas]] || [[Lone Star Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Texas Woman's University]]\n| [[Texas Woman's Pioneers|Pioneers]] || [[Denton, Texas|Denton]] || [[Texas]] || [[Lone Star Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| {{sort|Texas Permian Basin|[[University of Texas of the Permian Basin]]}}\n| [[Texas\u2013Permian Basin Falcons|Falcons]] || [[Odessa, Texas|Odessa]] || [[Texas]] || [[Lone Star Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Tiffin University]]\n| [[Tiffin Dragons|Dragons]] || [[Tiffin, Ohio|Tiffin]] || [[Ohio]] || [[Great Midwest Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Trevecca Nazarene University]]\n| [[Trevecca Nazarene Trojans|Trojans]] || [[Nashville, Tennessee|Nashville]] || [[Tennessee]] || [[Great Midwest Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Truman State University]]\n| [[Truman Bulldogs|Bulldogs]] || [[Kirksville, Missouri|Kirksville]] || [[Missouri]] || [[Great Lakes Valley Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Tusculum College]]\n| Pioneers || [[Greeneville, Tennessee|Greeneville]] || [[Tennessee]] || [[South Atlantic Conference]]\n|-\n!scope=row| [[Tuskegee University]]\n| [[Tuskegee Golden Tigers|Golden Tigers]] || [[Tuskegee, Alabama|Tuskegee]] || [[Alabama]] || [[So