ats\n|rowspan=2| Marquette, MI\n| {{sortname|Men's|ice hockey|Northern Michigan Wildcats men's ice hockey}}\n| [[Western Collegiate Hockey Association]]\n|-\n| Skiing\n| [[Central Collegiate Ski Association]]\n|-bgcolor=lightgreen\n| [[Paine College|Paine]]\n| Lions\n| Augusta, GA\n| {{sortname|Men's|volleyball|nolink=1}} (2020)\n| [[Southern Intercollegiate Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n| [[Palm Beach Atlantic University|Palm Beach Atlantic]]\n| Sailfish\n| West Palm Beach, FL\n| Beach volleyball\n| [[NCAA Division II independent schools#Sports not in D-II|Independent]]\n|-\n|rowspan=3| [[Post University|Post]]\n|rowspan=3| Eagles\n|rowspan=3| Waterbury, CT\n| Bowling\n| [[NCAA Division II independent schools#Sports not in D-II|Independent]]\n|-\n| {{sortname|Men's|ice hockey|nolink=1}}\n| [[NCAA Division II independent schools#Sports not in D-II|Independent]]\n|-\n| {{sortname|Women's|ice hockey|nolink=1}}\n| [[New England Women's Hockey Alliance]]\n|-\n| [[Queens University of Charlotte|Queens (NC)]]\n| Royals\n| Charlotte, NC\n| {{sortname|Men's|volleyball|nolink=1}}\n| [[NCAA Division II independent schools#Sports not in D-II|Independent]]\n|-\n| [[Queens College, City University of New York|Queens (NY)]]\n| Knights\n| Flushing, NY\n|data-sort-value=\"Fencing\"| Fencing<br>(Women's only)\n| [[National Intercollegiate Women's Fencing Association]]\n|-\n| [[Quincy University|Quincy]]\n| Hawks\n| Quincy, IL\n| {{sortname|Men's|volleyball|nolink=1}}\n| [[Midwestern Intercollegiate Volleyball Association]]\n|-\n| [[Roberts Wesleyan College|Roberts Wesleyan]]\n| Redhawks\n| North Chili, NY\n| Bowling\n| [[East Coast Conference]]\n|-\n|rowspan=2| [[Saint Anselm College|Saint Anselm]]\n|rowspan=2| Hawks\n|rowspan=2| Goffstown, NH\n| {{sortname|Men's|ice hockey|nolink=1}}\n| [[Northeast-10 Conference]]\n|-\n| {{sortname|Women's|ice hockey|nolink=1}}\n| [[New England Women's Hockey Alliance]]\n|-\n| [[St. Augustine's University|Saint Augustine's]]\n| Falcons\n| Raleigh, NC\