outhern Connecticut]]\n| [[Southern Connecticut Fighting Owls|Fighting Owls]]\n| New Haven, CT\n| {{sortname|Women's|gymnastics|nolink=1}}\n| [[Eastern College Athletic Conference]]\n|-\n| [[Southern New Hampshire University|Southern New Hampshire]]\n| Penmen\n| Manchester, NH\n| {{sortname|Men's|ice hockey|nolink=1}}\n| [[Northeast-10 Conference]]\n|-\n| [[Spring Hill College|Spring Hill]]\n| Badgers\n| Mobile, AL\n| Beach volleyball\n| [[NCAA Division II independent schools#Sports not in D-II|Independent]]\n|-bgcolor=#ffa0a0\n| rowspan=2 | [[College of Staten Island|Staten Island]]\n| rowspan=2 | Dolphins\n| rowspan=2 | Staten Island, NY\n| Men's indoor track\n| rowspan=2 | Independent (playing on a<br>[[City University of New York Athletic Conference]] schedule)\n|-bgcolor=#ffa0a0\n| Women's indoor track\n|-\n| rowspan=2 | [[Stonehill College|Stonehill]]\n| rowspan=2 | [[Stonehill Skyhawks|Skyhawks]]\n| rowspan=2 | North Easton, MA\n| {{sortname|Men's|ice hockey|nolink=1}}\n| [[Northeast-10 Conference]]\n|-bgcolor=lightgreen\n| {{sortname|Women's|ice hockey|nolink=y}} (2021)\n| [[New England Women's Hockey Alliance]]\n|-\n| [[University of Tampa|Tampa]]\n| Spartans\n| Tampa, FL\n| Beach volleyball\n| [[NCAA Division II independent schools#Sports not in D-II|Independent]]\n|-\n| [[Texas A&M University\u2013Kingsville|Texas A&M-Kingsville]]\n| Javelinas\n| Kingsville, TX\n| Beach volleyball\n| [[NCAA Division II independent schools#Sports not in D-II|Independent]]\n|-\n| [[Texas Woman's University|Texas Woman's]]\n| Pioneers\n| Denton, TX\n| {{sortname|Women's|gymnastics|nolink=1}}\n| [[Midwest Independent Conference]]\n|-\n| rowspan=2 | [[Tusculum University|Tusculum]]\n| rowspan=2 | Pioneers\n| rowspan=2 | Tusculum, TN\n| Bowling\n| [[East Coast Conference]]\n|-\n| {{sortname|Men's|volleyball|nolink=1}}\n| Independent\n|-\n| [[Urbana University|Urbana]]\n| Blue Knights\n| Urbana, OH\n| {{sortname|Men's|volleyball|nolink=1}}\n| data-sort-value=\"Independent\"| [[N