den.\n\n==External links==\nPattern 1\n*[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5lAsRCRapsE&t=44s Opening lines of Ferdowsi's ''Shahnameh''] recited in Persian. 1.1.11\n*[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OcQHSg_YZ6I Saadi's ''Ban\u012b '\u0100dam''] recited in Persian by Amir Ghaseminejad. 1.1.11\n\nPattern 2\n*[http://ganjoor.net/hafez/ghazal/sh3/ Hafez's ''Shirazi Turk''] Persian text, and recitations by Fereidoun Farahanduz, Soheyl Ghassemi, and Mohsen Layle Kuhi. 2.1.16\n*[https://blogs.harvard.edu/sulaymanibnqiddees/2012/11/06/rumi-i-do-not-recognize-myself/ Rumi's ''Neither a Christian nor a Jew''] recited in Persian by Bahman Sharif (text and translation supplied). 2.1.16\n*[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1crLioGCgAs Rumi's ''Neither a Christian nor a Jew''] recited in Persian (another version). 2.1.16\n*[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i4KXoeyubXk A do-bayti] sung by a village boy to a traditional melody. 2.1.11\n*[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g-68naSDpNk Googoosh singing \"Bridge\"] 2.1.11\n*[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5eHQVEzvSsA&list=LLfSd1XGM9B6-mjab_jT5k7g&index=976 Rudaki's ''B\u016b-ye J\u016by-\u0113 M\u016bliy\u0101n''] sung by [[Marzieh (singer)|Marzieh]] and [[Gholam-Hossein Banan]] 2.4.11 (but to the rhythm 3.1.11)\n*[https://ganjoor.net/moulavi/masnavi/daftar1/sh1/ Opening of Rumi's ''Mystical Masnavi''] recited by Mohammad Qanbar 2.4.11\n*[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4tSfqUuipU8 Rumi's ''Mystical Masnavi''] sung by [[Mohammad-Reza Shajarian]]. 2.4.11\n\nPattern 3\n*[https://magepublishers.com/wp-content/uploads/Hafez/rendevous_p.mp3 Hafez's ''Wineflask in hand''] recited in Persian by the poet [[Nader Naderpour]]. 3.1.15\n*[http://ganjoor.net/hafez/ghazal/sh26/ Hafez's ''Windflask in hand''] recited in Persian by Fereidoun Farahanduz, Soheyl Ghassemi, and Mohsen Layle Kuhi. 3.1.15\n*The first stanza of [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jpfX1T6XFNY \"Arise and Bring Fur\"] sung by the singer [[Giti Pashaei]]. 3.3.14\n*[https://www.youtube.co