e_producer   = \n| producer             = [[Songyos Sugmakanan]] <br/> Kriangkrai Vachiratamporn <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.marketingoops.com/media-ads/my-ambulance-romantic-fantasy-drama/|title=\u0e16\u0e2d\u0e14\u0e23\u0e2b\u0e31\u0e2a\u0e25\u0e30\u0e04\u0e23 \u201cMY AMBULANCE \u0e23\u0e31\u0e01\u0e09\u0e38\u0e14\u0e43\u0e08\u0e19\u0e32\u0e22\u0e09\u0e38\u0e01\u0e40\u0e09\u0e34\u0e19\u201d \u0e17\u0e33\u0e44\u0e21\u0e14\u0e31\u0e07\u0e1a\u0e19\u0e2d\u0e2d\u0e19\u0e44\u0e25\u0e19\u0e4c \u0e43\u0e19\u0e22\u0e38\u0e04\u0e04\u0e2d\u0e19\u0e40\u0e17\u0e19\u0e15\u0e4c\u0e25\u0e49\u0e19\u0e08\u0e2d|work=\u0e21\u0e32\u0e23\u0e4c\u0e40\u0e01\u0e15\u0e15\u0e34\u0e07\u0e2d\u0e39\u0e1b\u0e2a\u0e4c|date=2019-08-27|access-date=2019-10-31}}</ref> <br /> Suwimon Techasupinan\n| news_editor          = <!-- Content editor or editors of a current affairs/political show such as Newsnight. -->\n| location             = [[Thailand]]\n| cinematography       = \n| animator             = \n| editor               = <!-- Film editors -->\n| camera               = <!-- Either Single-camera or Multi-camera -->\n| runtime              = 45 minutes\n| company              = The One Enterprise <br /> [[Nadao Bangkok]]\n| distributor          = \n| budget               = \n| network              = [[GMM Grammy|One31]] <br /> LINE TV <br /> Dimsum Asia\n| picture_format       = \n| audio_format         = \n| first_run            = <!-- The nation in which the series first aired, if different from country parameter -->\n| released             = <!-- {{Start date|YYYY|MM|DD}} -->\n| first_aired          = {{Start date|2019|09|06}}\n| last_aired           = {{End date|2019|010|26}}\n| preceded_by          = \n| followed_by          = \n| related              = <!-- To be used only for remakes, spin-offs, and adaptations -->\n| website              = <!-- Remove or comment out this parameter line completely if URL exists on or is moved to Wikidata; use |website_title= to change the display title. -->\n| production_website   = https://tv.line.me/myambulance\n| production_website_title = My Ambulance \n}}\n\n'''My Ambulance''' ({{lang-th|\u0e23\u0e31\u0e01\u0e09\u0e38\u0e14\u0e43\u0e08\u0e19\u0e32\u0e22\u0e09\u0e38\u0e01\u0e40\u0e09\u0e34\u0e19}}; {{RTGS|''Rak Chut Chai Nai Chukchoen''}}) is a 2019 [[Thai language|Thai]] drama series starring [[Davika Hoorne]], [[Sunny Suwanmethanont]], and [[Wongravee Nateetorn]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thestandard.co/gdh-2019-projects/|title=\u0e42\u0e0a\u0e27\u0e4c\u0e1d\u0e35\u0e21\u0e37\u0e2d\u0e23\u0e38\u0e48\u0e19\u0e40\u0e01\u0e4b\u0e32 \u0e41\u0e25\u0e30\u0e40\u0e1b\u0e34\u0e14\u0e42\u0e2d\u0e01\u0e32\u0e2a\u0e43\u0e2b\u0e49\u0e04\u0e19\u0e23\u0e38\u0e48\u0e19\u0e43\u0e2b\u0e21\u0e48 \u0e01\u0e31\u0e1a 8 \u0e42\u0e1b\u0e23\u0e40\u0e08\u0e01\u0e15\u0e4c\u0e1b\u0e23\u0e30\u0e08\u0e33\u0e1b\u0e35 2019 \u0e08\u0e32\u0e01\u0e04\u0e48\u0e32\u0e22 GDH|date=2018-10-13|website=THE STANDARD|language=th|access-date=2019-10-18}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.daradaily.com/news/84078/read/|title=\u0e23\u0e27\u0e21 10 \u0e2a\u0e1b\u0e2d\u0e22\u0e25\u0e4c \"\u0e23\u0e31\u0e01\u0e09\u0e38\u0e14\u0e43\u0e08\u0e19\u0e32\u0e22\u0e09\u0e38\u0e01\u0e40\u0e09\u0e34\u0e19\"|date=2018-08-30|website=daradaily|language=th|access-date=2019-10-30}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thethaiger.com/thai/entertainment-th/%E0%B9%83%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%88-%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B2-%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%84%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%81%E0%B9%81%E0%B8%9F|title=\u0e43\u0e2b\u0e21\u0e48 \u0e14\u0e32\u0e27\u0e34\u0e01\u0e32 \u0e1a\u0e17\u0e1a\u0e32\u0e17\u0e04\u0e19\u0e23\u0e31\u0e01\u0e41\u0e1f\u0e19\u0e43\u0e19 \u0e23\u0e31\u0e01\u0e09\u0e38\u0e14\u0e43\u0e08\u0e19\u0e32\u0e22\u0e09\u0e38\u0e01\u0e40\u0e09\u0e34\u0e19|date=2019-09-30|website=The Thaiger|language=th|access-date=2019-10-30}}</ref> It is aired on [[GMM Grammy|One31]] from September 6 to October 26, 2019 and has 16 episodes. The series is produced by [[Nadao Bangkok]] and  directed by Naruebet Kuno.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.matichon.co.th/entertainment/news_1664556/|title=My Ambulance \u0e23\u0e31\u0e01\u0e09\u0e38\u0e14\u0e43\u0e08\u0e19\u0e32\u0e22\u0e09\u0e38\u0e01\u0e40\u0e09\u0e34\u0e19|date=2018-09-10|website=Matichon|language=th|access-date=2019-10-30}}</ref>\n\n==Plot==\nPeng ([[Sunny Suwanmethanont]]), an emergency center resident, and Tantawan ([[Davika Hoorne]]) have been in love for 15 years, mainly because they own a magical power between them which make Peng able to go to Tantawan when she calls him. One day, they got into a traffic accident and Thantawan is seriously injured. When she woke up, she lost her memory of the accident. Unbeknownst to her, the truth about the accident is hidden by Peng and all people around her. <br />\nA young and heart-warming intern, Chalan ([[Wongravee Nateetorn]]) appeared in her life and reminded her of the same feeling she once had for Peng. While her magical power with Peng has been weakening, Chalan has started to have the magical power leading to her confusion - who is the one for her. During this time, Peng also met a new girl named Paebii ([[Kanyawee Songmuang]]), who has a crush on Peng and came to the hospital as an ambulance driver to get closer to him.\n\n==Cast==\n===Main character===\n* [[Davika Hoorne]] as Tantawan Popboribun\n** Sawanya Paisarnpayak as young Tantawan\n* [[Sunny Suwanmethanont]] as Parama Otwaphan (Peng)\n** [[Vachirawit Chiva-aree]] as young Peng\n* [[Wongravee Nateetorn]] as Mahatmutra Sakulsirichai (Chalan)\n\n===Supporting character===\n* [[Kanyawee Songmuang]] as Paebii Phibulsawatdi\n* Putthipong Assaratanakul as Thara Thadalaksa (Dao)\n* Krit Amnuaydechkorn as Tiwkaow Popboribun\n* Ponlawit Ketprapakorn as Chonlathorn Khayanwongsa (Liwan)\n* Napat Chokejindachai as Wangkorn Hankul (Lek)\n* Paweenut Panakorn as Tikka\n* [[Thiti Mahayotaruk]] as Taai\n* Machida Sutthikulphanich as Khim\n\n===Cameo===\n* Lukkhana Siriwong as Peng's mother\n* Nitmon Ladapornphiphan as girl with heart disease\n* Buppa Suttisanon as Tantawan's mother\n* Nophand Boonyai as Tantawan's father\n* Varit Hongsananda as Chao\n* [[Banjong Pisanthanakun]] as psychiatrist\n\n== Soundtrack==\n* Ice Paris & [[Nichaphat Chatchaipholrat|Pearwah Nichaphat]] - ''Rak Tit Siren (Love Siren)'' <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://music.trueid.net/detail/4YBwdnvV0j5W|title=\u0e40\u0e15\u0e49\u0e19\u0e01\u0e31\u0e19\u0e17\u0e31\u0e49\u0e07\u0e40\u0e21\u0e37\u0e2d\u0e07! \u0e23\u0e31\u0e01\u0e15\u0e34\u0e14\u0e44\u0e0b\u0e40\u0e23\u0e19 \u0e44\u0e2d\u0e0b\u0e4c \u0e1e\u0e32\u0e23\u0e34\u0e2a \u0e41\u0e1e\u0e23\u0e27\u0e32 \u0e13\u0e34\u0e0a\u0e32\u0e20\u0e31\u0e17\u0e23 \u0e22\u0e2d\u0e14\u0e27\u0e34\u0e27\u0e40\u0e15\u0e23\u0e35\u0e22\u0e21\u0e17\u0e30\u0e22\u0e32\u0e19 100 \u0e25\u0e49\u0e32\u0e19\u0e27\u0e34\u0e27 (\u0e21\u0e35\u0e04\u0e25\u0e34\u0e1b)|date=2019-09-06|website=TrueID|language=th|access-date=2019-10-30}}</ref>\n* Billkin - ''You Are My Everything'' <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://lifestyle.campus-star.com/entertainment/178032.html|title=\u0e1a\u0e34\u0e27\u0e01\u0e34\u0e49\u0e19 \u0e1e\u0e38\u0e12\u0e34\u0e1e\u0e07\u0e28\u0e4c \u0e1c\u0e39\u0e49\u0e17\u0e35\u0e48\u0e23\u0e49\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e25\u0e07 You Are My Everything \u2013 \u0e23\u0e31\u0e01\u0e09\u0e38\u0e14\u0e43\u0e08\u0e19\u0e32\u0e22\u0e09\u0e38\u0e01\u0e40\u0e09\u0e34\u0e19|date=2019-08-24|website=Campus Star|language=th|access-date=2019-10-30}}</ref>\n* [[Sunny Suwanmethanont]] & [[Wongravee Nateetorn|Sky Wongravee]] - ''Love Message'' <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://music.guchill.com/love-message-%E0%B8%8B%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%88-%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B8%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%93%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%98%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%97%E0%B9%8C/|title=Love Message \u2013 \u0e0b\u0e31\u0e19\u0e19\u0e35\u0e48 \u0e2a\u0e38\u0e27\u0e23\u0e23\u0e13\u0e40\u0e21\u0e18\u0e32\u0e19\u0e19\u0e17\u0e4c (Ost.\u0e23\u0e31\u0e01\u0e09\u0e38\u0e14\u0e43\u0e08\u0e19\u0e32\u0e22\u0e09\u0e38\u0e01\u0e40\u0e09\u0e34\u0e19)|date=2019-09-09|website=Guchill|language=th|access-date=2019-10-30}}</ref>\n* [[Davika Hoorne|Mai Davika]] - ''Tok Lum Rak (Heartbeat)''\n* [[Kanyawee Songmuang|Thanaerng Kanyawee]] - ''Mai Penrai Rok (It's OK)'' <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://music.guchill.com/%E0%B8%84%E0%B8%87%E0%B9%84%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%88%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%9B%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%84%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%81-%E0%B8%95%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%B2%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B4/|title=\u0e04\u0e07\u0e44\u0e21\u0e48\u0e40\u0e1b\u0e47\u0e19\u0e44\u0e23\u0e2b\u0e23\u0e2d\u0e01 \u2013 \u0e15\u0e49\u0e32\u0e40\u0e2b\u0e19\u0e34\u0e07|date=2019-09-29|website=Guchill|language=th|access-date=2019-10-30}}</ref>\n* Ice Paris - ''Rak Tit Siren (Love Siren) (Midnight Version)'' <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thethaiger.com/thai/entertainment-th/songs-th/mv-%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%94%E0%B9%84%E0%B8%8B%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%99-midnight-version|title=MV \u0e23\u0e31\u0e01\u0e15\u0e34\u0e14\u0e44\u0e0b\u0e40\u0e23\u0e19 Midnight Version|date=2019-10-19|website=The Thaiger|language=th|access-date=2019-10-30}}</ref>\n* Friday - ''Nao Ni (This Winter)''\n* Scrubb - ''Khao Kan Di (Well)''\n* Buachompoo Sahavat - ''Love Message''\n\n== References ==\n<references />\n\n== External links ==\n\n*[https://tv.line.me/myambulance My Ambulance - Line TV]\n*[https://www.facebook.com/NadaoSeries Nadao Series]\n\n[[Category:Television series by Nadao Bangkok]]\n[[Category:2019 Thai television series debuts]]\n[[Category:2019 Thai television series endings]]\n[[Category:Thai television soap operas]]\n[[Category:One31 television programmes]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Thai television drama series}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name            = My Ambulance\n| image                = \n| image_upright        = \n| image_size           = \n| image_alt            = \